|  C-13   | 1.289165E+01 |  5.658220E+00 |     1.1 [3]|
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|  C-nat  | 1.190463E+01 |  4.758178E+00              |
|-----------------------------------------------------|
|                                                     |
|-----------------------------------------------------|	 
|  Si-28  | 2.773700E+01 |  1.955980E+00 |  92.223 [4]|
|  Si-29  | 2.872800E+01 |  2.584133E+00 |   4.685 [4]|
